    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Trim, then chop your<strong> green beans</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
