    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>warmed rice</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 3 min or until the prawns are cooked through – this is your <strong>smoky Spanish-style king prawns & rice</strong></p>",
