    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the prawns are cooking, cut your lemon[s] into wedges and combine a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice </strong>with your <strong>mayo</strong>, the <strong>remaining grated garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> lemon</strong> <strong>aioli</strong></p><p>Add a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong> into the pan and give everything a good mix up</p>",
